metadata.name: GAIA
metadata.description:
She called out to the forests, her voice the gentle breeze stirring blades of grass amongst the sweet smell of flowers. Twilight in her eyes tells the story of a thousand dreamy sunsets giving way to the dark wilds of the night. Strong and fertile, the royal ground beneath her feet holds the secrets of life itself as the mother of creation marvels at the most beautiful of creatures. A butterfly lands but for a second, and in that moment, as her gaze meets yours, GAIA holds you and you know what it means to be alive.

The first owner of this artwork will receive a special NFT as a gift.
